pan&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;也以圆形为主，果肉、果核也呈圆状，皮青绿色，刺多而密，果核大，果肉少但细腻而味浓；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 9.8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Consolas; color: #212121;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 20.0%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 9.8pt;&quot; width=&quot;20%&quot;&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 20.0%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 9.8pt;&quot; width=&quot;20%&quot;&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 20.0%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 9.8pt;&quot; width=&quot;20%&quot;&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;/tbody&gt;\n&lt;/table&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 60.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Consolas; color: #212121;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: 24.0pt; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Consolas; color: #212121;&quot;&gt;3.&lt;span style=&quot;font: 7.0pt &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &#39;Arial&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;）谷夜套：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;肉特别细腻，其甜如密，核尖小为&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &#39;Arial&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;&amp;ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;食家&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &#39;Arial&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;所欢迎，为价最高的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: 24.0pt; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Consolas; color: #212121;&quot;&gt;4.&lt;span style=&quot;font: 7.0pt &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;一种榴莲。泰国榴莲的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.so.com/s?q=%E4%BA%A7%E5%9C%B0&amp;amp;ie=utf-8&amp;amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #0063c8;&quot;&gt;产地&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;广阔，从中部暖武里府至动部&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.so.com/s?q=%E7%BD%97%E5%8B%87%E5%BA%9C&amp;amp;ie=utf-8&amp;amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #0063c8;&quot;&gt;罗勇府&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;，巴真武里府的榴莲曾获得冠军。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: 24.0pt; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Consolas; color: #212121;&quot;&gt;5.&lt;span style=&quot;font: 7.0pt &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.so.com/s?q=%E6%B3%B0%E5%9B%BD&amp;amp;ie=utf-8&amp;amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #0063c8;&quot;&gt;泰国&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;南部榴莲叫中部和东部的逊色，核&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.so.com/s?q=%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%89&amp;amp;ie=utf-8&amp;amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;color: #0063c8;&quot;&gt;大肉&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.0pt; color: #333333; background: white;&quot;&gt;小，但因成熟较迟，在其它榴莲盛季过&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Consolas; color: #212121;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: Consolas; color: #212121;&quot;&gt;6.&lt;span style=&quot;font: 7.0pt &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 1, 208, '2018-11-01 10:54:03', '2018-11-01 10:54:09', 1, 0, 'http://pic.58pic.com/58pic/17/44/77/38f58PICUNG_1024.jpg', '');
